---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Stainless Steel Wire Sock Hangers"
  description="Stainless steel wire sock hangers that hold multiple pairs of socks at once. Never rust, never break, and make laundry day easier."
>

  <section class="py-24 px-6 bg-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400 mb-4">Accessory · Sock Hangers</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-stone-800 leading-tight mb-6">Stainless Steel Wire Sock Hangers</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-stone-500 leading-relaxed">Hang more socks in less space. No more pegging individual socks — just clip and go.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">

      <div class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-800 mb-4">A smarter way to hang socks</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Sock hangers are one of those simple inventions that make you wonder why you didn't have one sooner. Instead of pegging each sock individually, you clip the hanger to your line and hang multiple pairs from it — saving time, space, and pegs.</p>
        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Made from stainless steel wire just like our pegs — so they'll never rust, never break, and will last as long as you need them to.</p>
        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">A brilliant gift for anyone who does a lot of laundry, or anyone trying to make their laundry routine more efficient.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-800 mb-4">Why you'll love them</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-stone-600 text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-600 font-bold">✓</span> Hang multiple pairs of socks from one hanger</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-600 font-bold">✓</span> Saves space on the clothesline</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-600 font-bold">✓</span> Stainless steel — never rusts or breaks</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-600 font-bold">✓</span> Works indoors and outdoors</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-600 font-bold">✓</span> Great gift idea</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <a href="https://www.biome.com.au/collections/wire-pegs" target="_blank" class="bg-stone-800 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-stone-700 transition-colors text-lg">Buy Sock Hangers at Biome →</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 px-6 border-t border-stone-100">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto flex gap-4">
      <a href="/products/jumbo" class="text-sm font-semibold text-stone-700 hover:text-stone-900 underline underline-offset-4">← Jumbo Pegs</a>
      <a href="/products" class="text-sm font-semibold text-stone-700 hover:text-stone-900 underline underline-offset-4">All Products →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>